    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    yaml,
    withr,
    rmarkdown,
    pillar,
    rlang,
    magrittr,
    tidyselect (>= 1.2.0),
    lifecycle
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
SystemRequirements: C++17
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp,
    BH
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
